      "writtenOn": "2019-05-11T00:41:55Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "the call chain here is getting pretty deep now. :-( i think we have:\n\n- Run\n- local\n- runLocalTests\n- runLocalRunner\n- startLocalRunner\n- ...\n\ni\u0027m not sure that it\u0027s easy to simplify, but i wonder if there are other names that would be clearer...",
      "revId": "2f0d8b56bb699cc6e6306a52e4ae9ae880b22cab",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
